entry.title: trained farm girls (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that in a weeklong contest during World War II, trained farm girls (pictured) were found to produce more enriched uranium than professional physicists?

entry.title: Nick Goiran (Wikipedia — did you know?)

entry.title: many fans died after falling onto a furnace (Wikipedia — did you know?)

entry.title: Jonas Mohammed Bath (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that Jonas Mohammed Bath was only able to obtain his freedom from slavery by purchasing another enslaved person to replace himself?

entry.title: Cavillargues medallion (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that the Cavillargues medallion depicts a Roman gladiatorial combat and possibly an official giving the signal for mercy?

entry.title: Rut Castillo (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that Rut Castillo was the only out LGBTQ rhythmic gymnast at the 2020 Olympics?

entry.title: Squib-class torpedo boats (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that the Confederate States Navy ordered six Squib-class torpedo boats from England, but they were never delivered?

entry.title: Jans der Enikel (Wikipedia — did you know?)
